latestIgtvVideos.title: YSL Makeup Unboxing
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
💄I was always Fascinated with my moms classic YSL lipsticks because of their unique & intricate design. So much so that every time I travelled overseas, on my return I would make sure to bring my mom a new YSL lipstick. Till date I keep up that tradition 🤗💄 Today I received  a surprise Package from @divya.sharma180986 & @sharmasheena who wanted to give me something for my birthday as we couldn’t be together this year and this is what I received !! I was  filled with so much excitement because I simply love @yslbeauty and all their products more so because of their elegant packaging💄 I don’t know how you know this Sheena & divya , but I love YSL & this is definitely one of the best surprises ever 🤗❤️ thank you from the bottom of my heart 🙏 #GarimaTewark #YSL #latebirthdaysurpise

My dear friend @ritika_jatin_ahuja & her incredible team at @bigboytoyz_india pulled off the dreamiest gender reveal for us. 💙 And my lovely sister my gender keeper @ankitatewari 

Ritika went above and beyond—even sourcing a car in the perfect shade of baby blue just for this moment. From the thoughtful details like the flowers, cake, and balloons to the love behind it all, every element made us feel incredibly special.

We’re so grateful for this unique and unforgettable celebration. 💫
